Package io.github.lengors.scoutdesk.domain.scrapers.specifications.filters

Interface ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchFilter

All Known Implementing Classes:
ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByQueryAndOwnerAndIgnoreCaseAndStrictModeEnabledFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceAndStatusFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceBatchAndStatusFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceOwnerAndStatusNotFilter
public sealed interface ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchFilter permits ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByQueryAndOwnerAndIgnoreCaseAndStrictModeEnabledFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceOwnerAndStatusNotFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceBatchAndStatusFilter, ScraperOwnedSpecificationBatchByReferenceAndStatusFilter
Sealed interface for batch filters on scraper-owned specifications. Permits various filter implementations for querying and filtering specification batches. This interface is used to define a common type for different filter implementations that can be used to filter batches of scraper-owned specifications.
